Task	                   Focus	                      Deliverable
---
1	Project setup + config + DB connection	App starts, loads .env, connects to Postgres
2	Migrations + User repository	        Users table created, CRUD operations
3	Domain + Service layer	Business        logic separated from DB
4	Handlers + Routing	                    API endpoints work (register/login)
5	Middleware + Auth protection	        JWT auth, protected routes
6	Task management + Transactions         	Create tasks, assign to users, use DB transactions
---

## Structure 
taskflow/
├── main.go    # Entry point, config loading, server start
├── config/
│   └── config.go  # Typed config struct + env loading
├── helper/
│   └── logger/logger.go   # the global logging
├── repository/
│   └── repository.go    # the DB global connection